CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 11, 1950, pg. 10, reads: "Pitt Deltas Frolic...Mu Chapter of Delta Sigma Theta Sorority, the University of Pittsburgh group, entertained classmates at the Brittle Breaker following the Pitt-West Virginia game last Saturday. All types of fun were available with games and dancing predominating.  Cordelia McMillon was chairman.  Pictured are guests Nick Temple, Jean Burrell, Dorothy Jackson and Rudy Riley. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Nick Temple, Jean Burrell, Dorothy Jackson, and Rudy Riley, posed around Delta Sigma Theta letters on table in interior for the sorority's Brittle Breaker event, another version
